  "caption": "The Brasserie at @naldhamhouse is the best way to end a work week.\n\nPictured 📸:\n1. Potato pavés with crème fraîche, chives\n2. Chicken skin crisp with whipped cod roe, caviar\n3. Smoked mortadella & adobo croquette with cheese emulsion\n4. Saucisson — dry-cured pork sausage with gnoccho fritto and cheese emulsion\n5. Hand-cut beef tartare with lavosh\n6. Wagyu cheeseburger with milk bun, cheese, lettuce, onion, pickle, and house-made burger sauce\n7. Steak frites au poivre with flank steak, fries, and creamy peppercorn sauce\n\n#sasenkalovesfood #SteakFrites #WagyuSteak #PeppercornSauce #FoodieBrisbane #BrisbaneEats #GourmetDinner #FoodLovers #BistroVibes #SteakNight #ModernDining #ComfortFoodElevated",
